-- Western Diet is Linked to Attention Deficit Disorder, Researchers Report
-- Jason Gale
-- 2010-07-29T02:22:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/western-diet-is-linked-to-attention-deficit-disorder-researchers-report.html

          
          
             Western-style diets in adolescents
may more than double the risk of attention deficit hyperactivity
disorder, scientists at the Telethon Institute for Child Health
Research said.  
 Their finding is published online in the international
Journal of Attention Disorders, the Perth, Western Australia-
based institute said an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        